The previously instantiated RFs above should have referenced component resource specifications of the 
composite RF specification for the vCDN. To avoid ambiguity the role attribute may be used to explicitly 
match an RF to a resource specification. 
Other resources and connectivity will be instantiated as provided in the composite RF specification for the 
vCDN.  
USE CASE 2 
Request creation of a flow on an existing topology. 
The diagram in Figure 2 has been taken from TR255A where the requirement is to create a new flow (red 
line) on the existing topology. 


